/>\n<br />\n三B級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">11,866元至14,064元</span><br />\n一級病人服務助理<span style=\"color: red;\">21,389元至25,199元</span><br />\n現時醫管局約有25,000名病人服務助理、運作助理及行政助理。<br />\n<br />\nEN <span style=\"color: red;\">20,610 至 43,783</span><br />\nRN <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMVEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=a639e848\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span>"},{"pid":"74f1c02d7a835b21e3ae769876aae3889833bb96","tid":1854474,"uid":310544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:35:25.000Z","msg":"中產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過又係仆街，呢個月21-23仲係武漢，斬撚咗佢全家啦"},{"pid":"e2d5b209380753e3343d1d1a912a4f4fcc65f7f6","tid":1854474,"uid":163937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"公司係附近 仆街了"},{"pid":"0aee50207480903a97eeb3ad3335eacc3ae45d31","tid":1854474,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,